  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "2nd firing; One is a victim",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Police said that a 27-year-old man died in a gunfight that took place in front of Palapitiya Hospital this (31) evening.",
        "A man from Kalakoda area of \u200b\u200bAmbalangoda was killed in a shooting by two people on a scooter.",
        "The police said that this is the fifth shooting that has taken place in Ambalangoda within five weeks and six people have died so far in those five shooting incidents.",
        "Meanwhile, the police said that two persons were injured and admitted to the Negombo General Hospital in the firing by two unknown persons on a motorcycle near the Negombo court.",
        "Police said that the injured in this incident which took place this afternoon (31) are 40 and 51 years old residents of Katana Temanhandiya area."
      ],
